Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:13.09,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\shad0\blur3\fad(200,200)}在回憶的八音盒中把你完全抽出來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:33.32,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\shad0\blur3\fad(200,200)}我鄰座的同學比較害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.65,0:01:38.95,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\shad0\blur3\fad(200,200)}每當她道謝時總是紅著臉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:43.87,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\shad0\blur3\fad(200,200)}這是我們倆想出來的秘密暗號
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:49.21,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\shad0\blur3\fad(200,200)}即使不再彼鄰 也一定能很快知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.38,0:01:53.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\shad0\blur3\fad(200,200)}新的一天還是會接踵而來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:58.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\shad0\blur3\fad(200,200)}我的小紙條請一定要傳遞到你手中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.93,0:02:01.51,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\shad0\blur3\fad(200,200)}啊啊 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:07.23,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\shad0\blur3\fad(200,200)}為什麼你看都不看就丟在一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.77,0:02:12.73,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\shad0\blur3\fad(200,200)}在回憶的八音盒中把你完全抽出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:18.36,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\shad0\blur3\fad(200,200)}長長的秀髮把你的表情都藏了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:23.33,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\shad0\blur3\fad(200,200)}為什麼我們就合不來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:31.25,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\shad0\blur3\fad(200,200)}明明我比任何人都了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:35.71,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\shad0\blur3\fad(200,200)}鄰座的你已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.51,0:22:25.83,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}もしもあの時そばにいたなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.99,0:22:41.67,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}今振り向いたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.07,0:22:45.35,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}なにもかもなくなっちゃいそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.57,0:22:48.31,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}そう　だから見ないふり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.69,0:22:51.13,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}唇きつく結ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.55,0:22:58.33,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}もしもあの時そばにいたなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.61,0:23:01.65,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}なんて言ったかな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.09,0:23:07.35,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ねぇ 君はなんて答えるの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.93,0:23:13.21,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}このままずっと何も知らないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.35,0:23:16.57,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}この距離感でいたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.63,0:23:22.28,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}少し不器用で　少し大人びて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.31,0:23:28.70,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}未完成な感情ばかりが心支配する
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:34.03,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}君はなんて答えたかな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.25,0:23:41.55,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}知りたい　知りたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.83,0:23:45.55,ED-jpn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}知りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.51,0:22:25.83,EDZ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}如果那時候你在我身邊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.99,0:22:41.67,EDZ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}若現在回過頭來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.07,0:22:45.35,EDZ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}彷彿將失去如今擁有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.57,0:22:48.31,EDZ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}沒錯 所以只能充耳不聞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.69,0:22:51.13,EDZ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}緊緊地閉上雙唇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.55,0:22:58.33,EDZ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}如果那時候你在我身邊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.61,0:23:01.65,EDZ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}你會說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.09,0:23:07.35,EDZ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}你會怎麼回答呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.93,0:23:13.21,EDZ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}如果一直這樣茫無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.35,0:23:16.57,EDZ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}這種距離感真想一直保持下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.63,0:23:22.28,EDZ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}有些笨拙 也有些成熟感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.31,0:23:28.70,EDZ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}未能眷屬的撕心感一直揮之不去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:34.03,EDZ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}你會如何回答呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.25,0:23:41.55,EDZ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我想知道 卻又不想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.83,0:23:45.55,EDZ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}但我還是想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.81,0:22:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fnFZXiYuan-M01\fs40\fad(500,1000)\pos(760,590)}大幅度的變動範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.46,0:00:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.94,0:00:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是說有事情想問我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.30,0:00:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,在大學的入學考試的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.40,0:00:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是關於泉學長的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以找他去約會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.68,0:00:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.16,0:00:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我大概知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.00,0:00:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,知道什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.84,0:00:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,相馬已經到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.14,0:00:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.06,0:00:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼 你在緊張嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.12,0:00:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.84,0:00:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,因為現在要去森川家 這也是沒辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.34,0:01:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就說不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.56,0:01:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.44,0:01:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊 這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.87,0:02:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,森川家？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎 快進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.53,0:02:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,早安 噗太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.39,0:03:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這星期都在想泉學長的事 害我完全睡不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,應該怎麼喊他去約會才好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.91,0:03:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 嚇到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我家非常老舊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,與其說是老舊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,因為房子很大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.85,0:03:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.87,0:03:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,都是以前的舊房子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.69,0:03:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,果然森川對烹飪挺有研究的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.57,0:03:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,說是烹飪 這只是普通的火鍋而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.41,0:03:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不知道做火鍋和烹飪東西有什麼區別
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.49,0:03:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,葉月連便當都是自己做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,還每天都幫妹妹做便當吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,早上媽媽需要出門工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,所以給他們做便當已經習以為常了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我的話可做不來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.07,0:04:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.99,0:04:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不過大學的入學考試那天很辛苦吧 居然下了大雪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,早上的時候真的有點慌張
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.41,0:04:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟車站裡的車都停運了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.79,0:04:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,都過了一星期 陰影處的雪都留著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.13,0:04:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,滿和弦做的雪人還在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.43,0:04:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但是大家都為我加油 所以做題時感覺很好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.47,0:05:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,要是因為下雪而落榜了 可真笑不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,之後還有考試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,大學的入學考試只是預防落榜而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,真正的一般入學考試是在下個月初
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,還很久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不 很快就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.99,0:05:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,時間完全不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,或許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,大家的志願都達成了 所以都很輕鬆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 我說了什麼奇怪的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.53,0:05:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到你也會說些抱怨話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,當然會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.29,0:05:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,因為被保送入學組和確定就職的背叛者們所包圍著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,要是早點知道你是這樣的話 在班上就能自然地聊天了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:05:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:05:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,話說 泉把葛絲都吃掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,吃肉啊 吃肉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,有人來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.59,0:06:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是陽斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.09,0:06:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是陽斗哥哥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.99,0:06:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.47,0:06:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,陽斗 來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.67,0:06:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好 那來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.93,0:06:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,要等吃完飯之後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord0\fs26\c&H182110&\pos(176,335)}學長 我們來約會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.99,0:06:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎麼說也太突然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:07:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\k30\c&H322726&\bord0\2a&HFF&\fs22\pos(262,299)}關{\k29}於{\k30}照{\k29}片{\k30}的{\k29}事{\k30}想{\k29}跟{\k30}你{\k29}道{\k30}謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\k34}{\c&H322726&\bord0\2a&HFF&\fs24\pos(250,382)}能{\k36}耽{\k30}誤{\k32}你{\k32}一{\k36}些{\k28}時{\k22}間{\k192}吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,太嚴肅了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,毫無約會的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H322726&\bord0\2a&HFF&\fs20\pos(177.6,448.5)\k19}我{\k19}想{\k19}好{\k19}好{\k19}謝{\k19}謝{\k19}{\k19}關{\k19}於{\k19}照{\k19}片{\k19}的{\k19}事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H322726&\bord0\2a&HFF&\fs20\k28\pos(359.2,448)}明{\k34}天{\k24}見{\k22}個{\k22}面{\k267}吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,大概這樣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,被拒絕的話該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要道謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.87,0:07:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺他會這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,噗太？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H322726&\bord0\2a&HFF&\fs40\pos(414.133,435.833)\frz329}我想好好謝謝你關於照片的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs30\frx26\frz325\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H3C&\pos(194.267,173.833)}已讀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H322726&\bord0\2a&HFF&\fs40\frz328.7\pos(724.133,621.833)}明天見個面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.41,0:07:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼這種時候馬上就讀了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:07:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,手到現在還在疼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.65,0:08:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,誰讓你不停在扔雪球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪你拒絕做投手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,因為天很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.49,0:08:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我也覺得很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不過夏目也不容易 還在備考
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.61,0:08:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說今天也要去補習班
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.41,0:08:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然很羨慕她能上大學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但是讓我去考大學的話完全沒可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.03,0:08:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,每天都要學習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H635657&\bord0\fs40\pos(308,232)\frz19.23}我想好好謝謝關於照片的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H635657&\bord0\fs40\frz19.23\pos(375.2,419.2)}明天見個面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\k39}{\c&H483333&\bord0\fs40\frz19.23\pos(485.6,526.4)\2c&H0000FF&\2a&HFF&}白天{\k30}的{\k74}話 {\k30}沒{\k66}問{\k62}題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,學長同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,現在還早 去別的地方轉轉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.29,0:08:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我還有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.67,0:08:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 明天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛來了件事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 你這週真難約啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,都說抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.99,0:09:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事 有事的話我一點都不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不過你看起來好像很介意的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什麼事情瞞著我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.87,0:09:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那你為什麼去書店買了考試的參考書
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你在淳久堂被我家奶奶看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.05,0:09:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我想學習一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.47,0:09:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,因為這是高中生的本職
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.71,0:09:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是想問這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 快說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,說了之後如果不成功的話就鬱悶了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你為什麼要買參考書
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我想參加考試
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.39,0:09:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:10:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 這件你還不穿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.97,0:10:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 還不穿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼 好可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.13,0:10:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,因為今天來朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐的朋友不是也有穿這個的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不是依子的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐也是時候認真打扮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,認真…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前有說過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.17,0:10:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,要認真考慮後再回覆的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我想報考夏目的第一志願大學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.65,0:10:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才不想說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不過既然你決定要做了 就加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.11,0:10:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我還算挺努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.19,0:11:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,小宮的事不管了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.11,0:11:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要在現在說起她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,因為感覺他們相處得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.53,0:11:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,瑛太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.27,0:11:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,和誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,和小宮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.29,0:11:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,哪裡有了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,整體上來說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.51,0:11:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,還是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,初中的時候 你也沒有能夠坦誠交談的女生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.93,0:11:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是有這種奇怪的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,與其擔心別人 你還是擔心下自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不要岔開話題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,森川家裡很有氣派
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,有點嚇著了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不 是嚇一大跳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不過都太晚了 反正都告白過了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.31,0:12:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,只能順其自然了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.91,0:12:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你這種方面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,說實話真的挺羨慕的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你這是在嘲笑我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,正因為對象是你 不然我都不會說考試的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,可別輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.47,0:12:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不是輸贏的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.97,0:12:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不過還是不要輸
